fun1=function(arg1,arg2)
{
s=c()
for(i in arg1:arg2)
 {if (i<5 | i >90)
   {s[i]=i * 10
   }else{
   s[i]=i*0.1
   }
}
s
}
fun1(arg1=3,arg2=50)
